E. Holman Clark https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/E._Holman_Clark 0 E. Holman Clark (1864–1925) was a British stage actor. He also appeared in seven silent films. He became famous for his annual Christmas performance as Captain Hook in J.M. Barrie's Peter Pan. E._Holman_Clark ( 1864 – 1925 ) was a_British_stage_actor . He also appeared in seven_silent_films .
